name: The Archdale Chair
description: The Archdale chair both elevates a room and enhances a dining experience with its scrolled back and gentle tapered legs. With legs finished in a stately shade of tinted beech, the Archdale finds the perfect balance between softness and sophistication. Choose from your favourite expertly crafted upholstery to flatter the curves, sweeps and flairs of the smart frame. Depending on the look you aspire to, the Archdale is available with or without arms to suit any interior.
